      <procstep>
        <procdesc>Dataset copied from the CD obtained from Washington, DC 2005

Fire stations were identified from lists published by the D.C. Fire and Emergency Management Services web site. A point shapefile was created by geocoding the addresses. These points were compared to the 1995 orthophotographs, the building footprint layer, and the D.C. Real Property Tax owner points for address and ownership information. The square suffix lot attribute was retained as the link to the data from the D.C. Office of Tax and Revenue. A link to the appropriate web site was provided for reference. The geocoded points were then moved to the center of the corresponding buildings and core attributes were added.

All DC GIS data is stored and exported in Maryland State Plane coordinates NAD 83 meters.</procdesc>
        <procdate>20010806</procdate>
